ecause entries cached in irrelevant positions skip the `checkComputable`\ncheck and must not be reused in relevant positions.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.CacheKey","kind":"structure","line":216,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.CacheKey","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.lean#L216-L225"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.Context.expectedType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">ToLCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">expectedType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The expected type of the expression that is currently being handled if available. This type is\nonly used to propagate potential borrow annotations as they are not propagated everywhere by the\nelaborator.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.Context.expectedType","kind":"def","line":214,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.Context.expectedType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.lean#L214-L214"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/ToLCNF.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.ToLCNF.Contex